==Digital example==
Compare the ''[[Basmala]]'', the beginning verse of the ''{{transl|ar|DIN|Qurʾān}}'' with all diacritics and with the ''rasm'' only. Note that when ''rasm'' is written with spaces, spaces do not only occur between words. Within a word, spaces also appear between adjacent letters that are not connected, and this type of ''rasm'' is old and not used lately.

