==Historical example==
The Kufic [[Samarkand Qur'an|Samarkand Qurʾan]] that was from 1869 to 1917 in St. Petersburg shows almost only ''rasm'': Sura 7 ''(Al-Aʿaraf),'' verses 86 & 87, of the Samarkand Qur'an, written in unadorned ''rasm''.

